title: Banged Up Abroad - Season 5
description:
Banged Up Abroad - Season 5

This series tells the stories of people who, through naivety, stupidity or plain bad luck have been caught smuggling drugs or another illegal item theyâ€™ve been tricked into carrying through customs. Other adventurers have strayed too far off the beaten track and found themselves hostage to guerrilla forces. Follow these individuals as they find themselves falling deeper into an inescapable downward spiral, from their initial motivation for the trip to their moment of arrest. Their capture, navigation of an incomprehensible legal system, time in incarceration and the traumatic blow the experience has on their relationships with family and friends are all profiled in this eye-opening series.

Ep 1 - Istanbul
Ep 2 - Iraq
Ep 3 - Tokyo
Ep 4 - Bangkok
Ep 5 - Spain
Ep 6 - Panama
